OL,3,CDoctors, teachers and soldiers to be
OL,4,Cawarded above-inflation pay rise
OL,6,FPay rises will be awarded to NHS
OL,7,Fworkers, teachers and most members of
OL,8,Fthe armed forces, the government has
OL,9,Fannounced after the latest review of
OL,10,Fpublic sector pay.
OL,12,FDoctors and teachers in England will
OL,13,Freceive a 4% increase, according to
OL,14,Fstatements released by ministers on
OL,15,FThursday afternoon, while other NHS
OL,16,Fworkers will get 3.6%.
