OL,4,Cawarded above-inflation pay rise
OL,6,FOther NHS workers in England,
OL,7,Fincluding nurses, midwives and
OL,8,Fphysiotherapists among other frontline
OL,9,Fworkers, will receive a 3.6% pay
OL,10,Fuplift, effective from April 1, Health
OL,11,FSecretary Wes Streeting said.
OL,13,FNHS staff who are members of the GMB
OL,14,Funion are being balloted about whether
OL,15,Fthe pay increase is acceptable,
OL,16,Faccording to the union.
OL,18,FThe increase for teachers will also be
OL,19,Fawarded to school leaders, according
OL,20,Fto Education Secretary Bridget
OL,21,FPhillipson.
