OL,4,Cawarded above-inflation pay rise
OL,6,FAn additional #615 million of funding
OL,7,Fwill be provided to schools this
OL,8,Ffinancial year to help them with the
OL,9,Fcosts of pay awards for staff, she
OL,10,Fadded, roughly equivalent to 3% of the
OL,11,Fpay rise.
OL,13,FSchools will be required to fund the
OL,14,Fother 1% of the pay rise through
OL,15,F"improved productivity and smarter
OL,16,Fspending", according to the Education
OL,17,FSecretary.
